elements.name: Como autor creo un tag, y un post con ese tag asignado

steps.name: I send a signal to user 6 containing "logged"
I go to new tag form
I send a signal to user 6 containing "creating tag"
I create a tag with name "$name_1"
I send a signal to user 6 containing "tag created"
I go to new post form
I send a signal to user 6 containing "creating post"
I create a post with title "$name_2" and content "$string_1"
I send a signal to user 6 containing "posting"
I send a signal to user 6 containing "post created"

name: Crear un post taggeado, y buscarlo en el listado de administracion filtrando por tag
